My friends and colleagues made me. My team made me. My inspirations made me. I am nothing without them. I owe all of this to them. 
I love NY comedy. Raw, unfiltered, no bullshit, tell it to you straight, just like the people. The scene lost its way for a little. It got soft, needy, it started to value applause over laughs. Well we‚Äôre deading that nonsense right now. That‚Äôs done. Back to the roots of what made us the greatest comedy city in the world. Back to not giving a fuck. Back to NY. The comeback begins...
